nice'n'shiny little island town at the seaside. In reality, Truman was an
unwanted pregnancy. His father, Christof, a reckless TV-Producer whom he

which life is live. So, everyone around poor Truman is an actor with a
little headphone in the ear. One day, Truman accidentally bumps into a
